Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.43,0:00:18.40,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:29.86,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.11,0:00:36.79,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:47.92,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:56.85,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.13,0:01:08.74,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.02,0:01:20.63,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:26.47,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.75,0:01:36.27,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.35,0:01:48.24,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(100,110)}Ep. 27 - Riding the Kite
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.99,0:02:10.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,At that moment, I was carried away\Nby thoughts of Lucy's illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.16,0:02:28.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.48,0:02:36.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alarmed by Little's shrieking I suddenly heard,\NI dashed towards where the shrieking came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.23,0:02:49.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You again!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.95,0:02:51.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Take this! 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:55.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you bully Little?!
Comment: 0,0:02:57.30,0:02:58.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.37,0:03:12.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.71,0:03:14.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She threw up, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:15.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:19.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But because she didn't eat anything,\Nthere wasn't much to throw up with. 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.15,0:03:20.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She looks in pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.33,0:03:22.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right... Now, if you'd allow me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.30,0:03:31.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Vomiting is also a consequence of high fever,\Nso you shouldn't be worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:35.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, does it hurt anywhere, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.49,0:03:37.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:39.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:04:01.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I swear... For how long is that quack\Ngoing to make me wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.19,0:04:12.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:16.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Hurts! Hell!
Comment: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:22.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, say, Doctor Deighton not finished yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He'll have to stay by Lucy-May's side\Nfor a while, it seems.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.23,0:04:30.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My sister is in extremely poor health now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.19,0:04:35.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor promised he'll yank my tooth out before.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.72,0:04:38.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If he doesn't hurry to yank it out soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.10,0:04:41.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Callous. How most callous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:52.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine! I'll go get another doctor.\NRight! That's right! I'll do just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, Kate?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:11.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little got hurt. The goatling, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:16.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Both got bitten by that black dog of Mr. Pettywell!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.49,0:05:18.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, how cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.03,0:05:21.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You think Dr. Deighton\Nknows how to heal the dog's wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.49,0:05:25.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You want Doctor to treat Little's wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.20,0:05:26.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be rude, I imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.69,0:05:29.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But that's awful! Look at his neck, for instance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:32.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, it's bleeding heavily. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:34.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, where's Doctor Deighton?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.91,0:05:36.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He's checking on Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:41.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If Little dies, Lucy-May would feel totally dejected. 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.12,0:05:43.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try asking doctor just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.34,0:05:45.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please do, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.20,0:05:49.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And where were you\Nwhen this was all happening? 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, you're a baby dingo, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:57.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know you're not supposed to die,\Neven if that black dog took it out on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:05:59.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You just can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.79,0:06:08.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Still sleeping tight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:13.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, ma'am,\NLucy-May will definitely recover.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:14.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.91,0:06:16.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.84,0:06:17.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.17,0:06:18.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have some tea in the other room. 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.58,0:06:20.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:23.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good idea. I'll gladly have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:39.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:45.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.63,0:06:47.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The disease spread over to Little as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.62,0:06:50.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He got in a fight with Mr. Pettywell's black dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.53,0:06:52.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why would they need to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:55.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see it all so I can't know for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:57.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it seems, the black dog assaulted the goatling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And he tried to save it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:01.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really so?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.70,0:07:03.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The baby goat also got bitten in the leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.83,0:07:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, there ain't no dingo in Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:12.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it could be that dingo blood is flowing in his veins,\Nbut he's a true dog, a friend to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:15.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But man, he's been roughed up badly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.00,0:07:18.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted Dr. Deighton to see if he can help Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:20.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No need. I'll do that myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:23.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor allowed me to use his disinfectant alcohol. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:25.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, no need, no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:27.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take a look at Little's injury right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.18,0:07:35.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It annoys me as hell, but going to the nearest doctor\Nwould be simpler, after all! 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.60,0:07:48.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, this one's gonna burn a little.\NEndure it bravely. You're a boy, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:51.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.88,0:07:55.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Doctor, Doctor!\NPlease hurry up to yank out my tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.20,0:07:57.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Haven't I told you before I'm no dentist?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.62,0:07:59.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you shouldn't move, Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.59,0:08:02.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:03.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.98,0:08:06.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you're treating the dog's skin. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,After he got bitten by your black dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.53,0:08:11.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By my dog? Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! That black dog bit Little!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.11,0:08:18.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's rubbish!\NWhy'd he wanna bully such a tiny little Johnny?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.53,0:08:20.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my own eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.02,0:08:21.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I even hit him with a stick for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you hit with a stick?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.08,0:08:27.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The black dog... 'Cause he's the one at fault here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.76,0:08:30.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My Happy is such an unfortunate fella.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.12,0:08:34.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wherever he goes, he's made a butt of,\Nwith no means of explaining himself. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:37.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you insinuating that what I said was a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.08,0:08:43.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not... Just that there was no one else watching\Nto corroborate your claim. 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:44.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How barbaric!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.22,0:08:49.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! It started hurting again!\NDoctor, I beg you! Yank it out sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:54.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to wait a little\Nuntil I'm done with tending to this patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:58.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You should've helped me first,\Nrather than this dirty mutt!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.90,0:09:03.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In my line of work, I always examine my patients\Non the "first-come-first-served" basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.27,0:09:06.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All right, that's done! Yes. 'Aight...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:08.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And up. How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.11,0:09:11.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good, you'll be fine here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.30,0:09:13.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.99,0:09:15.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.11,0:09:18.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you're trying to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.99,0:09:21.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, that's one cute fella you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.47,0:09:24.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then, you still wanna get that tooth yanked out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:27.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna put an end to this pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.05,0:09:29.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, then I guess we've no choice but to yank it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.10,0:09:32.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, which tooth was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:33.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:35.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, move the hand away now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, is this the one that hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,N-no, it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.89,0:09:44.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... No, not that again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.91,0:09:47.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But this one was already shaky enough. 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.13,0:09:47.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that either. Still somewhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:54.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.83,0:09:55.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:10:01.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the very same finger that the filthy dog\Nwas licking just a moment ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.69,0:10:02.46,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I s'pose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:04.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please wash it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.19,0:10:06.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't see any filth.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.96,0:10:10.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?\NThat dog... That dog licked it, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.39,0:10:13.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I really ought to? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:18.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course you should! Go wash it real clean now.\NJust faster, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very well... Sure, sure, sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.69,0:10:31.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, that was amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.49,0:10:33.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And what do you need that bamboo for?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.68,0:10:34.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.82,0:10:36.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll use this to make a kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:38.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A kite? Like the one that you fly in the sky? 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.25,0:10:42.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. I promised Lucy I'd make a kite for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.50,0:10:45.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So that she'd get well soon\Nand we go fly it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:48.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Back in England, you used to make them often.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:52.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This bamboo is a little different\Nfrom bamboo in England.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's still good enough for flying. 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.26,0:10:57.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're making it for Lucy,\Nso you want this kite to soar real high?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.51,0:10:58.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.61,0:11:07.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That should do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:11.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's finally about to begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.70,0:11:12.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.52,0:11:16.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.45,0:11:19.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please open your mouth wide one more time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.65,0:11:23.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Strangely, the pain seems to have subsided somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.38,0:11:27.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, still, this was not an easy decision to make. 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.50,0:11:30.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows if it doesn't start hurting like before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:33.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.38,0:11:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.62,0:11:39.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Listen here, it's gonna hurt a bit now.
Comment: 0,0:11:39.91,0:11:42.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.58,0:11:45.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A bit more, a bit... Just bear with it a little longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Need you... Not to resist so strongly... 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.81,0:11:51.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ow! Ow! Ow!\NCome on, be a good boy and open your mouth now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.62,0:11:54.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be biting others' hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.79,0:11:55.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch! Ouch! Ouch! Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.90,0:12:00.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,'Aight, can relax now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.17,0:12:02.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You sure didn't make it any easier for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:06.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.08,0:12:06.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.46,0:12:13.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor! That... That tooth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.30,0:12:15.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.59,0:12:19.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?! That tooth! Nothing was wrong with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.72,0:12:20.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:24.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This tooth... was...\NWas next to the one with the caries!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:25.56,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.56,0:12:30.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That tooth was next to it...\NNext to it... Next to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:34.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You damned quack!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.09,0:12:50.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.16,0:12:52.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh, I'm hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:12:55.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, wait just a bit. It's almost ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.90,0:12:58.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Father. Have you heard about\Nwhat happened to Mr. Pettywell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.75,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:02.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It was absolutely funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:03.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton pulled out\Ntwo of Mr. Pettywell's teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Two?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:09.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:12.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But of those, only one was with caries! 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.00,0:13:17.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You know, Kate, I'm not really finding it one bit funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:23.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I mean... I mean, he first pulled out\Nthe tooth that was never hurting!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell broke into tears then!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really, really don't understand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, it's finally here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:34.18,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, invite Doctor Deighton and Ben inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:36.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And please tell them I'm sorry for the delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:45.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, is that true Mr. Pettywell\Ngot two teeth pulled out today?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:49.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's what happened.\NAnd it sure was amusing, so amusing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.50,0:13:54.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't see how that could be amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:57.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for making you wait, please come to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.99,0:13:59.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Got it. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.77,0:14:01.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, did you hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:02.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really feel all that hungry today.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:08.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you that tired, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.91,0:14:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:13.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I still hope you can help Lucy get better soon. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.59,0:14:16.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? For that cause, I'll be happy to do my best. 
Comment: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.04,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.32,0:14:21.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Seems a lot like a proper kite already.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:26.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, what about are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.34,0:14:27.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't seem lively at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:41.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, so, you see, Mr. Pettywell's mouth\Nwas chock-full of bad teeth. 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I couldn't tell for sure\Nwhich tooth was actually hurting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:46.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you didn't do that on purpose, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.21,0:14:52.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not in this life! That was but a slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:55.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Even I can't be that mean-spirited!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:56.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.59,0:15:10.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.33,0:15:12.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I need to feed Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.60,0:15:16.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry about it,\NKate fed him long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you still have a fever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.50,0:15:21.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't be up yet. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.69,0:15:23.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go check on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.82,0:15:25.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sorry for the trouble, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:32.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy still seems pretty sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:47.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,God, please do something\Nto make Lucy's illness go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.88,0:16:08.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look for Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:14.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, I've always been a quack,\Nto a much greater extent than I ever imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.09,0:16:24.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose, the peak comes tonight.\NIf the fever doesn't subside by the morning... 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.99,0:16:28.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing much to be worried about, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.88,0:16:32.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought, I want to become a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.39,0:16:35.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Being able to save people's lives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:38.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other job that marvelous, right? 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I suppose. I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:11.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I fell asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.70,0:18:16.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I checked yesterday,\Nher breathing was already very placid. 
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.70,0:18:22.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose so.\NThe fever is also much milder now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.39,0:18:30.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's best that we let her sleep\Nthrough this afternoon as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.88,0:18:33.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure she'll get better. I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.20,0:18:35.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finished it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:37.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Finally!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.00,0:18:42.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.20,0:18:44.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And how does it look for Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.20,0:18:57.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.20,0:19:00.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:05.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've finished the kite.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.59,0:19:07.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.16,0:19:11.27,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I used the strings made in England,\Nso those are very long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:12.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And it'll fly mighty high!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.49,0:19:15.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Will you let me fly it, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:16.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:19.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Get better soon and we'll fly it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.09,0:19:23.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave it here for now. Okay?\NIt's for you to recover sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.50,0:19:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:43.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Yeah, good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've overslept beyond belief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:47.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, you went to see Lucy-May, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.56,0:19:49.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Seems to me like she is better than yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.93,0:19:52.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.10,0:19:52.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.13,0:19:54.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go take a look myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.35,0:19:56.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Just as I thought. Hm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.83,0:20:06.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:25.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little, if you hang out around here,\Nyou'll also be covered in mud!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Little recovered mighty fast, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.48,0:20:33.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I really admire you, bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.22,0:20:34.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.20,0:20:37.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You spent yesterday making this kite, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.02,0:20:40.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. But I don't think\Nit was something particularly admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.55,0:20:45.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you made it,\Nhoping to cheer Lucy up with it, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.09,0:20:46.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,More or less.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.50,0:20:50.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I, for one, couldn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.00,0:20:56.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You covered for Lucy in looking after\Nthe goats and Little, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.81,0:21:00.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But my negligence ultimately led to Little getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.50,0:21:03.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All the more reasons\Nwhy that black dog is one nasty sucker.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.46,0:21:04.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.01,0:21:09.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So, you want me to come again\Nin one week from today?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.72,0:21:11.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.12,0:21:13.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By that time, I hope...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.30,0:21:16.77,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be done with the rest,\Nso there'd only be a roof to install.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.51,0:21:21.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As for the roof, I though about shingling it\Nwith eucalyptus bark, this time. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I'll leave it up to you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:26.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Mr. Jamling.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.99,0:21:29.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Working hard as usual, Ben?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.46,0:21:33.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In a week from today,\Nwe've agreed on me installing a roof here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:38.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we'll also have to ramp up the pace\Nat which we're making bricks, won't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Keep up the good work, Ben.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:44.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, I'd think Lucy\Nis of little to no help whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:49.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But with her gone, we'll hardly be able\Nto actually make 30 bricks a day. 
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.10,0:21:52.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something happened to Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.87,0:22:04.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,...To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:09.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.00,0:22:12.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,the vow made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.91,0:22:18.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.55,0:22:24.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.64,0:22:30.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:36.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.62,0:22:42.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.50,0:22:48.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,all around my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.32,0:22:54.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.53,0:23:03.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.00,0:23:14.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.96,0:23:19.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dad asked you to prepare some tea\Nbecause Mr. Jamling is visiting us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:19.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.48,0:23:26.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My... That soup, is it for Tob to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:29.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's for Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.05,0:23:30.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,For Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.61,0:23:32.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.05,0:23:34.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She just said she's starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:35.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.43,0:23:38.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Did she recover, at last?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:41.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she's a-okay now.
